Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.32,0:00:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,(第2次見面跟第3次見面)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.69,0:00:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,(都一樣全裸到早上為止)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.46,0:00:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,(鷲尾芽衣)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.51,0:00:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.15,0:00:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天真的是很抱歉那個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.95,0:00:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,發生那種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.86,0:00:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是喝太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你喝的太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.64,0:00:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,頭很痛對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.81,0:00:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.74,0:01:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我睡了之後\N就感覺痛快多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.01,0:01:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.78,0:01:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.98,0:01:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.78,0:01:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,喝太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.66,0:01:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天的事情你不要跟別人講哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.03,0:01:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎麼可能跟別人說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.37,0:01:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.67,0:01:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.99,0:01:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,先去吃午飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.60,0:01:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我先午休一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.20,0:02:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你們也要吃好休息一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.24,0:02:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那我先去休息一下了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.31,0:02:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不吃飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,今天吃便當
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.26,0:02:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真好啊新婚餐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.26,0:02:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我便當好像沒帶忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.37,0:02:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真是令人頭大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.98,0:02:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你忘記拿便當了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.05,0:02:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,幫大忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.26,0:02:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉\N我丈夫承蒙各位照顧了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.16,0:02:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊才是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.43,0:03:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,今天幾點回來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,今天不用加班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,很快就可以回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.41,0:03:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那我在家裡做好飯等你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.68,0:03:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我丈夫就拜託你們了
