Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.82,0:03:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你們相處的挺好的
