Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我們兩個人想的是一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什麼樣的表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.04,0:21:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,弄進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.44,0:21:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.94,0:21:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我先把它取下來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.91,0:21:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,挺難為情的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.59,0:21:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,弄進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.75,0:22:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.22,0:22:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,很有感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.42,0:22:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.28,0:22:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.09,0:22:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我舒服一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.16,0:23:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.31,0:23:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.39,0:23:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
