Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.18,0:23:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.61,0:23:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.32,0:24:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.10,0:24:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.33,0:24:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡激烈一點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.87,0:24:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.80,0:24:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那就從後面來了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.24,0:24:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.18,0:24:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,拔出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.26,0:24:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,想要弄進來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.79,0:24:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.31,0:24:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.18,0:25:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,這張是很漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.86,0:25:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.13,0:25:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.67,0:25:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.54,0:25:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.38,0:25:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好激烈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.02,0:25:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.70,0:25:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.14,0:26:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.48,0:26:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.12,0:26:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.56,0:26:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.17,0:27:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.87,0:27:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.39,0:27:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真的那麼厲害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.39,0:27:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,根本停不下來
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.53,0:27:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.41,0:27:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的很想從後面來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.65,0:27:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.49,0:27:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.16,0:28:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,有點不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.39,0:28:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼東西不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.23,0:28:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,來這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.66,0:28:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,突然打開開關了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.68,0:28:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,有點不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.05,0:28:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,很厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.62,0:29:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼突然的\N舔我我真的嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.23,0:29:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.68,0:29:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.33,0:29:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.78,0:29:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,很喜歡胸部嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.28,0:29:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,最喜歡胸部了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.30,0:30:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.14,0:30:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,這個地方很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.23,0:30:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.34,0:30:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.24,0:31:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.31,0:31:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.86,0:32:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.40,0:32:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.07,0:32:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.92,0:33:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.63,0:33:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有點不妙 好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.57,0:33:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.64,0:33:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.78,0:33:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是好舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.93,0:34:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.57,0:34:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,有點不妙  好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.51,0:34:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.85,0:34:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.24,0:34:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.91,0:34:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,才剛剛射了沒多久\N居然還有這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.88,0:35:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.52,0:35:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,身體還是很誠實的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.40,0:35:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,有點不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.80,0:35:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.90,0:35:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.08,0:35:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真是可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.30,0:35:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,(昨天)
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.20,0:35:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那個交貨日期的話
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.31,0:35:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,下週吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.21,0:36:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.84,0:36:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但是據我們這邊所知
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.58,0:36:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,至少還是要一週的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.29,0:36:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣子啊那沒有問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.46,0:36:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 明天我們再去拜訪一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.26,0:36:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.20,0:36:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,下午3點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.20,0:36:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.04,0:36:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,明天的時間就這定了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.98,0:36:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,下午3點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.35,0:36:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.15,0:36:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,說的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.55,0:36:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那就3點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.59,0:36:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.66,0:36:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我先掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.54,0:37:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,這一件就交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.31,0:37:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,大夥注意
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.48,0:37:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,多虧了各位的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.45,0:37:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這個月
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.05,0:37:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我們創造了\N這個部門有史以來
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.99,0:37:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,最棒的業績
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.60,0:37:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,以此為紀念
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.53,0:37:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,今天下班之後
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.93,0:37:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,打算請你們去喝一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.24,0:37:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你們覺得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.94,0:37:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.37,0:37:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.24,0:37:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那就定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.94,0:37:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.28,0:37:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,山口呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.28,0:37:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.85,0:37:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.92,0:37:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我很期待酒會
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.99,0:37:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們就一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.96,0:37:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,說的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.49,0:37:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,多虧了各位的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.76,0:37:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,明天就要好好慰勞一下各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.13,0:38:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.50,0:38:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事啦我請客
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.77,0:38:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,想喝啥喝啥
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.14,0:38:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.64,0:38:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那就喝個痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.54,0:38:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼都可以吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.84,0:38:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,當然啦我們要痛快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.34,0:38:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.28,0:38:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們去喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.68,0:38:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼既然決定好的話
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.08,0:38:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的工作就趕緊搞完它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.05,0:38:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.89,0:38:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,等會就好好喝個痛快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.29,0:38:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.11,0:38:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你是新婚沒多久
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.01,0:38:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你得先提前跟你妻子講一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.42,0:38:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,這倒也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.19,0:39:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真痛
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.76,0:39:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,已經下來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.76,0:39:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.73,0:39:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,喝太多了真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.80,0:39:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.54,0:39:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如果被別人知道就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.48,0:39:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不可以暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.95,0:39:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟你是新婚沒多久
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.22,0:39:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用擺出這樣的表情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.96,0:39:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,本來沒有這種打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.86,0:39:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不過你還不是做了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.94,0:39:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要我也來
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.18,0:39:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但是已經
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.15,0:40:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你不願意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.45,0:40:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,還是把它當做一場夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.56,0:40:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你笑什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.20,0:40:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你剛不是在笑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.50,0:40:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.14,0:40:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.55,0:40:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,如果做這種事情的話
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.92,0:40:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.06,0:40:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你指哪方面
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.49,0:40:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,會忍不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.71,0:41:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣很不妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.01,0:41:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你的手沒地方放嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.53,0:41:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,還是很柔軟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.03,0:41:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,比你妻子還柔軟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.30,0:41:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,這種沒得比呀
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.07,0:41:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.77,0:41:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是在摸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.17,0:41:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這個算特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.98,0:41:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.81,0:41:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,像這麼漂亮的胸部\N應該不存在了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.55,0:41:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就喜歡我的胸部對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.22,0:41:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.29,0:41:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是這麼回事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.79,0:41:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.84,0:42:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,可以舔一下乳頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.71,0:42:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.05,0:42:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,果然的胸部好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.87,0:42:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你舔的方式好淫蕩
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.33,0:43:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.10,0:43:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,有點不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.11,0:43:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,真是可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.07,0:43:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.51,0:43:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.41,0:43:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,很喜歡這樣弄頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.45,0:43:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.15,0:43:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛才做過愛
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.56,0:44:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你還這麼堅硬
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.13,0:44:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.93,0:44:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,花心是不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.60,0:44:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊也要填嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.55,0:44:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.75,0:44:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,變硬了很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.56,0:44:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.30,0:44:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.47,0:44:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.75,0:44:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.28,0:44:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.48,0:45:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我什麼都沒有在做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.12,0:45:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,可是這樣子會忍不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.63,0:45:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,這是說明 我口交很厲害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.56,0:45:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.27,0:45:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,有點不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.83,0:45:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那我挺開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.88,0:45:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,有點不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.29,0:45:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不行要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.70,0:45:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,別那麼輕易的就射出來
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.77,0:45:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.81,0:45:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,根本忍不住
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.11,0:45:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才不是沒有成功嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.21,0:46:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這次我想要乳交
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.48,0:46:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,乳交嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.72,0:46:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,來把腰停起來
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.63,0:46:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.00,0:46:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,很柔軟
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.80,0:46:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,有感覺了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.14,0:46:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.98,0:46:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,看不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.38,0:46:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,很柔軟
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.42,0:46:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,很堅硬
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.16,0:46:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,越來越硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.13,0:46:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.67,0:47:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,都看不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.78,0:47:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.48,0:47:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我還沒怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.92,0:47:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子的話實在是
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.59,0:47:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.06,0:47:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,等等別這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.06,0:47:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.73,0:47:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,很難搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.84,0:47:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,喂你好
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.87,0:47:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.81,0:47:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我看你沒有聯我\N我就打電話過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.81,0:47:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.55,0:47:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.61,0:47:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,今天在公司裡面的飲酒會上
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.95,0:47:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,喝多了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.69,0:47:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.39,0:47:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你一個人在酒店嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.06,0:47:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定是一個人在酒店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.96,0:48:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那不然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.47,0:48:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.94,0:48:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,很久沒有喝那麼多了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.01,0:48:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,有點頭痛
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.98,0:48:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺你怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.18,0:48:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.58,0:48:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,果然還是
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.58,0:48:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.99,0:48:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.19,0:48:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,休息一下就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.29,0:48:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你應該打個電話過來啊\N搞得我都擔心你了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.43,0:48:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.23,0:48:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,真的喝多了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.04,0:48:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我當時就不省人事了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.81,0:48:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,有那麼誇張嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.81,0:48:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我在酒店裡面休息
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.88,0:48:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼怎麼了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.15,0:48:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是喝水嗆到了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.49,0:48:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.59,0:49:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,可能今天太勉強自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.96,0:49:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,喝到斷片了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.40,0:49:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊有點
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.90,0:49:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你這樣怎麼能行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.28,0:49:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣對身體不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.35,0:49:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,今天真的是太勉強自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.89,0:49:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,因為為了慶祝業績\N所以很多人都在狂歡
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.33,0:49:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這方面的話
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.00,0:49:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,慶祝什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.00,0:49:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,就是我們部門的那個業績很好
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.70,0:49:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這倒無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.11,0:49:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯是的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.94,0:49:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我被前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.54,0:49:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是別人敬酒給你\N你也不用每個都接呀
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.78,0:50:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,這個很難拒絕的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.19,0:50:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你就不能拒絕別人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.12,0:50:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這種拒絕不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.82,0:50:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,話雖如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.90,0:50:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能老是順著氣氛\N就一直喝個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.40,0:50:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.30,0:50:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我會注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.61,0:50:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我會好好注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.01,0:50:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.55,0:50:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定要了解自己的極限才行
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.02,0:50:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我會注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.09,0:50:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.06,0:50:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,還要花多長時間
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.23,0:50:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.96,0:50:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,總之我今天先在酒店休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.00,0:50:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,到時候就恢復一下就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.57,0:50:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.81,0:51:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.01,0:51:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那就再見
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.78,0:51:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那你要好好休息哦
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.91,0:51:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,休息完後會打電話給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.18,0:51:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.65,0:51:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,先掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.25,0:51:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.22,0:51:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.62,0:51:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.69,0:51:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.13,0:51:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.63,0:51:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.84,0:51:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你是說真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.77,0:51:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你剛剛不是說再見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.57,0:51:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.71,0:51:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.64,0:51:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛表現的太不自然了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.75,0:51:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不自然嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.05,0:51:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊跟平時的我不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.08,0:51:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.05,0:51:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.82,0:51:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,根本受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.95,0:51:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣不是挺興奮的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.26,0:51:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子興奮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.46,0:51:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但是暴露就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.99,0:51:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,發出聲音是我的問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.03,0:51:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不是這樣的問題好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.97,0:51:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,萬一暴露了怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.30,0:52:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.01,0:52:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才不是很自然的在對話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.78,0:52:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.78,0:52:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,都太可疑了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.91,0:52:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是更加那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.65,0:52:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,可這種事情還是很擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.15,0:52:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.42,0:52:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.67,0:52:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是累了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.61,0:52:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,像這樣子可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.01,0:52:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,搞笑
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.88,0:52:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,難為情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.41,0:52:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,有一點那個
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.45,0:52:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,但是很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.16,0:53:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才的擔心到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.77,0:53:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,可這樣子的話
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.77,0:53:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.75,0:53:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.27,0:53:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.30,0:53:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你很喜歡搞裡面對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.18,0:53:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真的挺舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.37,0:54:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.00,0:54:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很喜歡胸部啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.21,0:54:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,很喜歡胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.58,0:54:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.88,0:54:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,更喜歡我的還是你太太的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.11,0:54:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,這種怎麼能回答呢
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.78,0:54:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣子不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.72,0:54:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,真是體貼
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.22,0:54:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.39,0:54:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,越來越硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.06,0:54:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.67,0:54:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你只會說舒服兩個字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.17,0:54:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.58,0:54:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那就挺開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.54,0:54:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,吃的很舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.71,0:54:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你的肉棒越來越硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.82,0:55:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.59,0:55:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.75,0:55:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,剛剛才射過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.50,0:55:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.11,0:55:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什麼多喝一點啊\N（昨晚)
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.31,0:55:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,都第幾杯了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.01,0:55:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,有點
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.54,0:56:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那種我才不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.61,0:56:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,先喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.38,0:56:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,多喝點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.05,0:56:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真是沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.08,0:56:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼一來的話就喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.92,0:56:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你也一起喝呀
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.65,0:56:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底可以喝多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.86,0:56:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.93,0:56:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼好喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.33,0:56:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,能喝前輩喝酒 我很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.70,0:56:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,說的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.30,0:56:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我實在是沒有想到
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.77,0:56:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真的和厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.87,0:56:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你們也一起喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.91,0:56:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,很普通吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.71,0:56:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都很憧憬你的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.07,0:56:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有必要考慮那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.74,0:56:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.14,0:56:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.28,0:56:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,這個有搞頭
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.85,0:56:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.18,0:56:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是你酒量真好
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.12,0:56:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這太厲害了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.89,0:56:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,還能再多喝一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.86,0:56:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是很過分哎
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.49,0:56:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,這個人說話很過分唉
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.43,0:56:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真的很好喝哎
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.40,0:56:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.66,0:56:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,果然是我選的 真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.56,0:56:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是你
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.07,0:56:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這個可以有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.33,0:56:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊這裡面挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.87,0:57:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,乾杯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.74,0:57:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.91,0:57:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,新婚生活很幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.51,0:57:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,是的很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.18,0:57:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,來多喝點多喝點
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.38,0:57:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,來一起開心一下
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.02,0:57:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.09,0:57:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,第幾杯了已經
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.46,0:57:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你的眼睛都有點迷離了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.53,0:57:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.83,0:57:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.77,0:57:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哇厲害了一口悶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.97,0:57:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡還有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.37,0:57:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,還有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.71,0:57:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.71,0:57:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,有點
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.51,0:57:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,他喝倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.45,0:57:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.98,0:57:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,行不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.75,0:57:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,太太在等你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.89,0:57:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.36,0:57:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,拿點水來
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.16,0:57:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他什麼情況啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.46,0:57:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,多喝一點
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.63,0:58:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,喝太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.43,0:58:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就是說呀
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.53,0:58:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,沒要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.70,0:58:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.04,0:58:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊吧你那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.24,0:58:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.18,0:58:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,都到時間了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.22,0:58:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.59,0:58:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,等會我來
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.26,0:58:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,送回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.92,0:58:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.13,0:58:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.16,0:58:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.46,0:58:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,很累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.63,0:58:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.33,0:58:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那就先玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.37,0:58:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那就一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.94,0:58:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.34,0:58:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.71,0:58:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你們先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.41,0:58:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,時間也快不夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.21,0:58:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那就恭敬不如從命
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.45,0:58:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.61,0:58:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.98,0:58:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,去下一家
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.42,0:58:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.36,0:59:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是沒什麼好在意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.49,0:59:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經不想喝酒了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.30,0:59:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.10,0:59:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,想要重來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.24,0:59:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,重來一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.54,0:59:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.91,0:59:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,還挺可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.02,0:59:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,有人這樣說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.92,0:59:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不怎麼有人說
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.26,0:59:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.26,0:59:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.96,0:59:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼好笑的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.86,0:59:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.63,0:59:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟你太太怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.53,0:59:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,看了嗎說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.53,0:59:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定很在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.00,0:59:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,這有什麼好問的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.44,0:59:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟在公司裡面見過
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.41,0:59:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然發生了這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.68,0:59:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,果然還是
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.08,0:59:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,還是會很喜歡我妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.32,1:00:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.89,1:00:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,也不用反應那麼大吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.93,1:00:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我又沒問你奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.46,1:00:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.10,1:00:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,想讓他幸福的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.64,1:00:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我們約過的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.14,1:00:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但是新婚的話
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.71,1:00:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.21,1:00:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上的生活
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.58,1:00:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你們怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.68,1:00:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是說晚上嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.18,1:00:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼能這樣問呢
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.52,1:00:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,哪有這樣的機會詢問啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.22,1:00:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想要一個參考
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.63,1:00:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼參考的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.06,1:00:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴下我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.43,1:00:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,當然還是會有性生活啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.63,1:00:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有多少
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.83,1:00:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這有什麼好說啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.14,1:00:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,一週兩次嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.81,1:01:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,大概一個星期4次5次吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.61,1:01:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那豈不是很猛嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.12,1:01:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.36,1:01:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你的閨蜜嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.69,1:01:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,對我來說的話
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.56,1:01:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,應該能體驗到\N不同女生的區別吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.16,1:01:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼區別啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.60,1:01:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哪邊更舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.57,1:01:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,哪邊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.40,1:01:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,對可以比較出來的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.61,1:01:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我比較不出來
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.24,1:01:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這種比較比比較不出來
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.24,1:01:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.91,1:01:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是有經驗嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.75,1:01:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這種不好比較的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.68,1:01:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣是不行的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.72,1:01:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不能比較對吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.06,1:01:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是的無法比較
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.02,1:01:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.56,1:01:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.87,1:01:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這種
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.67,1:02:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,無法回答嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.45,1:02:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然說你更舒服但是
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.39,1:02:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你承認我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.32,1:02:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但我和我妻子是夫妻
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.36,1:02:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你害怕破裂嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.03,1:02:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,說不定會因此破裂
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.09,1:02:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼不就承認我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.23,1:02:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.73,1:02:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.27,1:02:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,有點不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.04,1:02:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,事到如今這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.98,1:02:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我更加
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.98,1:02:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服一點
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.72,1:02:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,要不再來一次
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.29,1:02:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你很露骨啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.36,1:03:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.06,1:03:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但是什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.57,1:03:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.64,1:03:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,更加
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.04,1:03:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.98,1:03:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你是這樣想的嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.01,1:03:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.15,1:03:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好柔軟啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.11,1:04:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,有點什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.61,1:04:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,身材真的好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.73,1:04:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了呀
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.37,1:04:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,很柔軟
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.27,1:04:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的很喜歡胸部呢
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.58,1:04:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你的胸部
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.34,1:04:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我最喜歡
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.88,1:04:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,誠實是件好事
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.52,1:05:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,看到這個我怎麼忍得住啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.79,1:05:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒打算忍耐對吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.49,1:05:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這倒也是
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.71,1:05:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,可以來親吻一下
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.32,1:05:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊有感覺了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.30,1:05:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,越來越硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.11,1:05:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,很難為情
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.44,1:05:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.06,1:06:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.97,1:06:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,很美味
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.51,1:06:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.18,1:06:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.37,1:06:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以高潮嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.25,1:07:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.96,1:07:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好難為情啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.67,1:07:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想搞
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.18,1:07:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,伸出舌頭
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.19,1:08:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.37,1:08:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.99,1:08:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你的乳頭都變硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.46,1:09:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,因為有感覺
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.25,1:09:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.92,1:09:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.23,1:09:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.10,1:09:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.07,1:09:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.78,1:09:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,有點不妙
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.62,1:10:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.17,1:10:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,已經這麼堅硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.60,1:10:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.54,1:10:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.11,1:10:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.38,1:10:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒有試過這招嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.68,1:10:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定沒有試過啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.95,1:10:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,太難為情了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.45,1:10:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,都看光了對吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.88,1:10:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.99,1:10:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,難為情嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.52,1:10:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.96,1:10:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,會很興奮的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.04,1:11:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,很難為情嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.40,1:11:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.33,1:11:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.88,1:11:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,越來越硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.61,1:11:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.63,1:11:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.26,1:11:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服哦這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.48,1:12:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.88,1:12:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,有點不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.85,1:12:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼敏感的嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.05,1:12:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.76,1:12:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.26,1:12:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,累了嗎已經
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.50,1:12:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那就來接吻吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.12,1:13:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害都濕透了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.86,1:13:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.45,1:13:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,有點忍不住
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.16,1:14:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,可以脫掉嗎
