Dialogue: 0,1:54:44.27,1:54:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼有感覺的嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:54:47.24,1:54:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,有感覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:54:58.32,1:55:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.99,1:55:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,有感覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:55:11.09,1:55:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,插進去了
Dialogue: 0,1:55:56.71,1:55:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:56:23.13,1:56:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,1:56:51.80,1:56:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好想要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:56:54.10,1:56:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,很想要嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:57:10.78,1:57:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:57:34.44,1:57:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:57:46.25,1:57:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:57:48.02,1:57:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊很舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:57:51.82,1:57:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,太舒服了
Dialogue: 0,1:57:56.26,1:57:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有點忍不住
Dialogue: 0,1:57:58.56,1:58:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那就射出來吧
Dialogue: 0,1:58:00.46,1:58:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,可以射出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:58:04.07,1:58:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,1:58:08.04,1:58:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,要射出來了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:11.78,1:58:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:58:35.00,1:58:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,射出來好多
Dialogue: 0,1:58:47.48,1:58:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,還抽得出時間見我嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:58:54.25,1:58:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,多弄一點
Dialogue: 0,1:58:56.45,1:58:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼跟什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:59:04.06,1:59:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:59:12.07,1:59:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,還有一點時間吧
Dialogue: 0,1:59:17.91,1:59:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我才剛射了一次
Dialogue: 0,1:59:21.28,1:59:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,就再玩一玩吧
Dialogue: 0,1:59:23.91,1:59:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,現在嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:59:29.39,1:59:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:59:32.79,1:59:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這算什麼呀